#

Bacon and Blue Cheese Guacamole

10 min
$10
320 kcal
Difficulty: 20%
Servings: 4

Allergens:

Dairy

Dietary Tags:

Gluten-FreeHigh-Protein

Cuisine:

American

Course:

Appetizer

Tags:

AppetizerSnackEasy

Description

A creamy, savory twist on traditional guacamole that combines crispy bacon and tangy blue cheese for a delightful dip.

Ingredients

  • ripe avocados: 2
  • bacon: 4 slices
  • blue cheese crumbles: 1/2 cup
  • lime juice: 2 tablespoons
  • salt: to taste
  • black pepper: to taste
  • cilantro (optional): 2 tablespoons
